high_descs: Turn left, then move left a little to face the sink drying rack.
Take the knife from the rack.
Move left a little to face the counter to the left of the drying rack.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Move right a little to face the sink basin.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move left a little to face the counter to the left of the drying rack.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Move right a little to face the sink. Look up to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave. Take the tomato from the microwave.
Move left a little to face the counter to the left of the drying rack.
Put the tomato slice to the left of the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink to your right.
Pick up the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the tomato on your right by the sink.
Slice the tomato in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink on your left.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the tomato on your right by the sink.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the microwave on top of the sink to your left.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave, take out the tomato and close the microwave.
Turn left and face the coffee maker to your right.
Place the tomato slice by the coffee maker in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot tomato slice by the coffee maker.

high_descs: turn around and move forward, going passed the sink and turn to face the counter to the left of the sink in front of the tomato
pick up the butter knife with the silver handle that is behind the sharp knife with the yellow handle
stay in front of the tomato holding the knife
slice half of the tomato
turn to the right and move close to the sink and stand to face the sink
put the knife in the sink
turn to the left and turn back to face the slice tomato
remove a slice from the tomato
turn to the right and move back in front of the sink and facing the microwave above the sink
open the microwave door, put the tomato inside the microwave, close the door, cook for 3 seconds, open the door of the microwave door and remove the tomato
turn to the left and move to the counter to the left of the sink and turn to face the tomato on the counter
put the slice of tomato to the left of what is left of the sliced tomato
anns.task_desc: put a cooked slice of tomato on the counter

high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter next to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look around for the tomato.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Go to the sink to the right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the sliced tomato.
Take one slice of tomato.
Go to the microwave above the kitchen sink.
Microwave the slice of tomato and then take it out.
Take the heated slice of tomato back to the kitchen counter with the rest of the tomato.
Place the heated slice next to the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Heat one slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter next to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the paring knife on the counter.
Move over to the left to the tomato on the white counter top.
Slice the tomato on the counter top.
Take the paring knife to the sink.
Place the paring knife inside the sink.
Move back to the counter top with the sliced tomato.
Take one slice of the tomato.
Take the slice of tomato to the microwave above the kitchen sink.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave and take it out.
Take the heated slice of tomato back to the white counter top.
Place the heated slice to the left of the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of tomato next to the rest of the sliced tomato.
